 Secure the Vault
Revoke the initial root token:

 
 
vault token revoke hvs.5bTWW0Xxiwg9jYJrp9G1hwwF
Configure Vault to start automatically with the system:

 
 
sudo systemctl enable vault
(Optional) Disable TLS Verification (for Development only):

If you encounter certificate verification issues during development, you can disable TLS verification:

 
 
export VAULT_SKIP_VERIFY=true
